OL,3,CCouncils in England risk losing
OL,4,Cpothole funding if they do not meet
OL,5,Cnew rules
OL,7,FEnglish councils risk losing up to a
OL,8,Fthird of their funding to fix potholes
OL,9,Fif they fail to demonstrate they are
OL,10,Fworking effectively, the Department
OL,11,Ffor Transport (DfT) has announced.
OL,13,FSome #525 million of the #1.6 billion
OL,14,Ffunding for local roads maintenance in
OL,15,Fthe 2026/27 financial year will be
OL,16,Fheld back unless authorities prove
OL,17,Fthey are spending the money
OL,18,Fappropriately.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/8
