OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1776175862
OL,3,CCouncils in England risk losing
OL,4,Cpothole funding if they do not meet
OL,5,Cnew rules
OL,7,FThis is up from #500 million of the
OL,8,Fsame amount during the previous 12
OL,9,Fmonths.
OL,11,FCouncils are required to publish
OL,12,Freports showing they are spending all
OL,13,Ftheir highways cash purely on road
OL,14,Fmaintenance, with long-term plans for
OL,15,Fprotecting roads.
OL,17,FThis includes having policies signed
OL,18,Foff by senior local authority members
OL,19,Fand training for highways teams.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/8
