OL,3,CCouncils in England risk losing
OL,4,Cpothole funding if they do not meet
OL,5,Cnew rules
OL,7,FRoads minister Simon Lightwood said:
OL,8,F"Drivers deserve smooth, safe
OL,9,Fjourneys, and we're making sure every
OL,10,Fpound goes straight into fixing roads
OL,11,Fand tackling potholes, not being spent
OL,12,Felsewhere.
OL,14,F"We've made it crystal clear that
OL,15,Fcouncils which fail to maintain their
OL,16,Froads will now risk losing up to a
OL,17,Fthird of their funding.
OL,26,@pD@AOUvD@AOU
