OL,3,CCouncils in England risk losing
OL,4,Cpothole funding if they do not meet
OL,5,Cnew rules
OL,7,F"And for the first time, we're giving
OL,8,Fcouncils multi-year funding so they
OL,9,Fcan plan properly and reverse a decade
OL,10,Fof decline in our roads."
