OL,3,CCouncils in England risk losing
OL,4,Cpothole funding if they do not meet
OL,5,Cnew rules
OL,7,FAA president Edmund King said it is
OL,8,F"right that councils are being
OL,9,Fscrutinised over their repair plans"
OL,10,Fas he urged them to "use their funding
OL,11,Fto resurface roads rather than simply
OL,12,Fpatch up their streets".
OL,14,FRAC head of policy Simon Williams
OL,15,Fsaid: "Ensuring money that is given to
OL,16,Fcouncils to improve their roads is
OL,17,Factually spent on roads is critical,
OL,18,Fso the government's focus on this will
OL,19,Fbe welcomed by drivers."
