OL,3,CCouncils in England risk losing
OL,4,Cpothole funding if they do not meet
OL,5,Cnew rules
OL,7,FIt was estimated last month that the
OL,8,Fcost of bringing pothole-plagued local
OL,9,Froads in England and Wales up to
OL,10,Fscratch had risen to a record #18.6
OL,11,Fbillion.
OL,13,FThe announcement comes a month after
OL,14,Fresearch by the Asphalt Industry
OL,15,FAlliance (AIA) found only 51% of the
OL,16,Flocal road network is reported to be
OL,17,Fin good condition.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
