PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1776175862
OL,3,CCouncils in England risk losing
OL,4,Cpothole funding if they do not meet
OL,5,Cnew rules
OL,7,FIt also claimed the estimated cost of
OL,8,Fbringing pothole-plagued local roads
OL,9,Fin England and Wales up to scratch has
OL,10,Frisen to a record #18.6 billion,
OL,11,Fbranding the situation "a national
OL,12,Fdisgrace".
OL,14,FIt claimed this shows extra investment
OL,15,Fto tackle potholes has failed to
OL,16,Fdeliver "noticeable improvements".
OL,18,FRoads are only being resurfaced, on
OL,19,Faverage, once every 97 years.
